2010-10-09 # 1.0

[CHG] The module is now extending the 'contents' module rather then the 'system.nodes' module.

[CHG] Markups are now extending the 'contents' markups.

[DEL] The `is_home_included` property and methods have been moved to the 'contents' module.

[DEL] The support for an associated image has been remove since the 'resources.images' module
can now add an associate image to any of the 'system.nodes' objects.

[DEL] The "Ã  la une" feature has been removed because it's easily replaced with an additional
content, which may be inherited, on the home page. 